snippet.title: Wordle, Dordle, Quordle, and Octordle Speedrun in 34.29 seconds (WR)
snippet.description:
This category of speedrun is called "Expordle":
Solve, in order, a non-Daily Wordle, Dordle, Quordle, and Octordle using the provided official website links for each variant. Moving onto the next variant is allowed once the final word / letter turns green.
Wordle: https://cubeythecube.github.io/wordle/
Dordle: https://zaratustra.itch.io/dordle
Quordle: https://quordle.com
Octordle: https://octordle.com
Wordle speedrun discord: https://discord.gg/qnrCZu3Tux
Wordle speedrun leaderboards: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/11Dhgra3HWUH0vEV8la-iA_Ao7dto4vrnG2g7oei-9DI
